metadata.name: Enchanted Place
metadata.description: In this busy and greedy world I am feeling uncomfortable. I don't like this crowded city and non stop traffic. I want some peaceful place, where i can enjoy my solitude, where i can talk with my true self, where I can take a test of real beauty of nature. One day during my journey... I found out this magical place... which is glowing with energetic lights and shining with sunset... I can name this place an ' Enchanted Place
